message.body: Hey! No worries about Pilates tonight. You rest up and get all better! I actually woke up today with a sore throat and am super tired so I need to take it easy too!
Oh and random question, but do you know how much hunter is selling those triangular prints with the eye for?
Oh no I hope you aren't getting sick!! I feel so much better but still coughing and breathing weird. The prints are 100 with frame but it's not triangular for the print
Also, I think some are up at Gush by VIX
Awesome! Thanks for the info! Going in with a client now!
Hey! Do you have any cornstarch?
Haha ok no worries!
None! I'm so surprised tho cause we usually do
Nate must have used it! Is it for your ricotta cake?
No I made that last night. I was gonna make a fruit sauce and I need a tablespoon of cornstarch
Mm fruit sauce
Yeah totally
I just want a topping for my ricotta cake
It's goooood
I really want to buy one of those eye prints from hunter!
I love that triangle frame though
Ricotta cake sounds amazing. I know the original is the only one with the triangle. People always ask about that
It's super cool
It looks so nice!
I really like the purplish color of the other one though
Yeah I think we wanna buy one
I like the print though it looks great
Sweeet. I want so many
I'll see what the dimensions are on the print. I think it's smaller than the cut out.
But don't know for sure
Cool! Let me know!
Are you feeling better today?
Fo sho.
